<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">الْمُسْلِمُ بِالْخِيَارِ:</span> إِنْ شَاءَ فَسَخَ الْعَقْدَ فِي الْجَمِيعِ وَإِنْ شَاءَ أَجَازَهُ فِي الْجَمِيعِ. وَهَل لَهُ الْفَسْخُ فِي الْقَدْرِ الْمُنْقَطِعِ وَالإِْجَازَةُ فِي الْبَاقِي؟ فِيهِ قَوْلاَنِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>خِيَارُ التَّفْلِيسِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> إِفْلاَسٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>خِيَارُ تَلَقِّي الرُّكْبَانِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> بَيْعٌ مَنْهِيٌّ عَنْهُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>خِيَارُ التَّوْلِيَةِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> تَوْلِيَةٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
